# cmusfm

> Scrobble tracks from the `cmus` music player to Last.fm.
> More information: <https://github.com/Arkq/cmusfm#configuration>.

- Initialize `cmusfm` and authorize access to your account:

`cmusfm init`

- Display help:

`cmusfm`
